text: Adelsdorf is a municipality in the district of Erlangen-Höchstadt, in Bavaria, Germany. ==Twin towns – sister cities== Adelsdorf is twinned with: * Uggiate- Trevano, Italy (1997) * Feldbach, Styria, Austria (2007) ==References== ==Other websites== * Coat of Arms History Category:Erlangen-Höchstadt
